SUMMARY:Israeli Dancing
DESCRIPTION:Join Chicago Israeli dancing\, led by Phil Moss and Penny Brichta\, and learn how to dance like an Israeli every Thursday night! For more information you can refer to chicagoisraelidancing.com The event is held in the Wiener Room and through Zoom. \n 
URL:https://bethemet.org/event/israeli-dancing-4-2/2026-03-26/
LOCATION:IL
CATEGORIES:Congregational Programs
