SUMMARY:Kahal Potluck Lunch
DESCRIPTION:If you are able to attend on Saturday morning\, please consider bringing a vegetarian\, nut-free dish or lunch item for all to enjoy. The potluck will take place in the Sanctuary and on LiveControl. Please also take a moment to jot down a list of ingredients that can be displayed with your dish for the benefit of those with food allergies. \nInstead of a potluck item\, feel free to donate to help offset the cost of purchasing food.
