SUMMARY:The Latest News with J Street's Jeremy Ben-Ami
DESCRIPTION:J Street President Jeremy Ben-Ami will be at Beth Emet on Thursday\, April 9 at 7:30 pm for a timely\, intimate conversation with Rabbi London about Israel\, the Middle East\, and how American Jews are navigating this unprecedented political moment.  As elections approach at hoome and in Israel\, we’ll discuss how we canhelp shape a future grounded in the Jewish values of justice\, peace\, and freedom. For security purposes\, please register here.
